metadata.name: The Stinker Gravelicker
metadata.description:
The stinking grave licker presents Through the visuality of a comic book cover, the moment in which a cemetery guard finds before him a creature that licks the tombs, awakening the souls of the dead. It is the presentation of a villain with absurd power honoring the classic tradition of characters in classic comics and at the same time poses a philosophical question that points to the dark side of our relationship with our dead and their memory.

is part of the EnlightningAdventures collection which illustrates the adventures of a strange character who seeks without hesitation to fill his existence with light through all kinds of occurrences and adventures.
